{
  "id": "adv_event_2408_01_05_01",
  "title": "敵はやっぱり",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――密着取材、最終日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Close Coverage‚ Final Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスのセンターは私よ\n真ん中に立つのは当然でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm ⅢX's center.\nIt's natural for me to stand in the middle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2000001192,
      "endTime": 7.1555329561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、ただの思考停止じゃん\n曲を大事にしない人は、センターに相応しくないでーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's just thoughtless.\nSomeone who doesn't value the song isn't suitable for center~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3666667859,
      "endTime": 15.7797277371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　franとkanaが喧嘩しているのに\nそんなに平然としていていいのかって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? Even though fran and kana are fighting‚\nis it okay for me to be so calm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9666667859,
      "endTime": 22.2924717824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "私達は固い絆で結ばれていると信じていますが\nなあなあの馴れ合いがいいとも思っていません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believe we're bound by strong bonds‚ but\nwe don't think that overly agreeable relationships are good either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5000001192,
      "endTime": 29.0849661112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "お互い、忌憚のない意見をぶつけ合いますし――\n時にはあんな風に、喧嘩になることだってありますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We clash with each other's frank opinions‚ and--\nsometimes it becomes a fight like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3000001192,
      "endTime": 36.3248302698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……本当に、たまにですけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Really‚ just occasionally though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.5333334525,
      "endTime": 39.208390196100005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、そのくらいにしておきなさい\n今回は……そうね、私もkanaと同意見よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of you‚ leave it at that.\nThis time… yes‚ I agree with kana too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4000001192,
      "endTime": 48.575533223099995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、今までの私達のイメージを崩したくないから……\nそうね、2コーラス目ではfranがこっちに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don't want to break our image up until now‚ so…\nYes‚ in the second chorus‚ fran should go over here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7666667859,
      "endTime": 58.0363265912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（な、なんとか誤魔化せた……か？）\n（良かった、どうなることかと思った……！！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（D-did we somehow manage to cover it up…?）\n（Thank goodness‚ I wondered what would happen…!!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2333334525,
      "endTime": 65.4772111495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "あー、やっと密着取材終わったー！！\nこれでカメラに追いかけられないで済むー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh‚ the close coverage is finally over!!\nNow we don't have to be chased by cameras!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7666667859,
      "endTime": 75.6075512807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "本当にね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8000001192,
      "endTime": 77.1581860542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "それにしてもさあ、あんた達、見てた？\n最後に喧嘩してた時の{user}の顔！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But anyway‚ you guys‚ did you see it?\n{user}'s face when we were fighting at the end!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3666667859,
      "endTime": 85.93031768009999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "こりゃ事務所クビになるな、再就職どうしようって\n絶望ぶりだったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like‚ \"I'm gonna get fired… How will I find another job?\"\nHe looked so desperate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1333334525,
      "endTime": 92.3920636733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さすがにそこまでは考えてませんでしたけど……\nでも本当に肝が冷えたんですからね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wasn't really thinking that far ahead…\nBut I really was scared out of my mind!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.6000001192,
      "endTime": 99.05857136249999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "ぷぷ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pfft…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2666667859,
      "endTime": 100.4134634177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "……ふ、くくっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Fu‚ fufu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.5999940157,
      "endTime": 102.10140299790001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "……あはは、あははははは！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ahaha‚ ahahahahaha!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2999970674,
      "endTime": 105.6791806459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "だって順調に仕事して仕事して曲作って終了、じゃ\n番組として面白くないじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mean‚ if it's just work‚ work‚ write the song‚ and done—\nthat wouldn't be an interesting show‚ would it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8666637341,
      "endTime": 114.5083413998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "だからkana達が、番組の盛り上げどころを\n作ってあげたって訳",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So kana and the others created the climax\nfor the show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6999970674,
      "endTime": 119.7409948587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "私のドッキリにGO出したのはまだ恨んでますけど\n仕掛け人をやりたい気持ちは、ちょーっと分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I still haven’t forgiven you for approving that prank on me‚\nbut I kinda understand the feeling of wanting to be the mastermind behind it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.9333304007,
      "endTime": 127.6442600806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……みなさんが喧嘩するのはいつも通りですけど\n喧嘩の内容は、いつもより真剣だったような……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True… you all fighting is as usual‚ but\nthe content of the fight seemed more serious than usual…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8333304007,
      "endTime": 136.7331266959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、私達がいつも馬鹿馬鹿しいことでしか\n喧嘩していないみたいじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That makes it sound like we only ever\nfight about ridiculous things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.9333304007,
      "endTime": 143.03487220600002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "これだけ撮れ高くれてやったんだから\nちゃんと新曲の宣伝しないと、許さないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we gave you this much good footage‚\nif you don't properly promote the new song‚ I won't forgive you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.2333304007,
      "endTime": 149.3057565291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "まったくよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.4999970674,
      "endTime": 151.2012800931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、貴方のせいで取材を受ける羽目になったのよ\n一緒になって、したり顔で頷いていないでちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the first place‚ it's your fault we had to accept the interview.\nDon't nod along with a smug face.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.4000102917,
      "endTime": 159.13672207989998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "もう散々文句聞いたわよ、そろそろいいでしょ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've heard enough complaints already‚ isn't it about time to stop!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.333343625,
      "endTime": 163.7272209405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（なんか……曲を作ってる時より息が合ってるな）\n（結局、三人を団結させる『敵』は俺だった訳か……はぁ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Somehow… they're more in sync than when they were making the song.）\n（In the end‚ the 'enemy' that united them was me… sigh.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.933343625,
      "endTime": 176.8931393861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二週間後　ライブバトル",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Two Weeks Later‚ Live Battle",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.9000102917,
      "endTime": 179.4200042407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.5333466768
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.6000101726
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
